  "title": "admin assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description & Requirements</strong></p><p>ob Description & Requirements</p><p>We are looking for a motivated and organized assistant to join our renovation team. You will be a key player in ensuring our office runs smoothly by providing essential administrative support.</p><p>Key Responsibilities:</p><p>· Handle general office tasks: answering phones, greeting visitors, and managing mail.</p><p>· Perform data entry and maintain accurate digital and paper filing systems.</p><p>· Assist with preparing documents, reports, and presentations using Microsoft Office.</p><p>· Help with scheduling meetings and managing office supplies.</p><p>· Support other teams with various administrative tasks as needed.</p><p>Who You Are:</p><p>· High school diploma or equivalent; additional certification in Office Administration is a plus.</p><p>· Some experience in an office environment is preferred, but we are willing to train the right candidate.</p><p>· Proficiency in Microsoft Office (Word, Excel, Outlook).</p><p>· Strong organizational skills and a keen eye for detail.</p><p>· Excellent communication skills and a professional attitude.</p><p>· Ability to work effectively both independently and as part of a team.</p><p>What We Offer:</p><p>4 off days monthly, rest days depend on schedule. able to work long hours and late in evenings and weekends</p><p>Competitive salary 3k and above</p><p>Positive and nurturing working environment</p><p>Work location: islandwide</p><p>Duration: permanent</p><p>Requirements</p><p>Qualifications - diploma or high school diploma</p><p>Work experience- at least one year working experience in related fields</p><p>Job type- full time</p><p>Required languages: English and able to communicate with mandarin speaking customers</p><p>If you have an interest in applying for this role, please WhatsApp me at 98198786 to apply. Only shortlisted candidates will be notified. Priority will be given to Singaporeans</p><p>Young hon Lim/ manager</p><p>Render private limited</p><p>EA licence no 15c7827</p><p>EA reg no R1550906</p>",
